Assistant Manager Communications
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 06:57:07
Ref. JB3045311
Job Description
This role involve the editing and writing of press releases for the Communication Manager, writing speeches, and having a good network of contacts in the Media industry.
Skills
Experience in writing speeches, press releases, editing, copy writing.
Have a broad network of contacts in the Media industry.
Have previously dealt with the Ministry of Affairs.
Bilingual preferably.
